  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FilterMapper
    Maps internal filter values to external, AutocompleteFilter values.
    PlaceDialogFragment.PlaceDialogListener
    Dialog listener interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GeoDataApiImpl
    GeoDataApi implementation for Places.
    PeliasFilterMapper
    Maps internal filter values to AutocompleteFilter values for the PlaceAutocompletePresenter.
    PlaceAutocompleteActivity
    Activity that provides auto-completion for places.
    PlaceAutocompleteView
    Compound view which displays search icon, autocomplete text view and clear button.
    PlaceDialogFragment
    Confirmation dialog shown to the user when a POI has been selected.
    PlaceImpl
    Represents a physical place selected from a com.mapzen.android.graphics.MapzenMap.
    PlaceImpl.Builder
    Builder class for PlaceImpl.
    PlaceIntentConsts
    Intent constants for PlaceAutocomplete and PlacePicker APIs.
    PlacePickerActivity
    Activity which displays a map and a dialog when the user selects a place on the map.
    PlaceStore
    In-memory store used to persist data for currently selected place.
    PointToBoundsConverter
    Constructs a LatLngBounds given a LatLng.
